data.description: Welcome to this fully renovated charming split-level home nestled near the Atlanta Motor Speedway in Henry County with a new roof, new appliances, new paint throughout, and new bathrooms!!!!! Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms this residence provides a thoughtfully designed layout to accommodate your lifestyle. The main level welcomes you with a warm and inviting atmosphere, featuring a bright living room, open dining area, and a well-appointed kitchen with all updated appliances with beautiful backsplash and countertops. The convenience of having two bedrooms and one full bathroom on this level ensures practicality and ease of living. Enjoy seamless indoor-outdoor living with direct access to the backyard deck from the dining room, creating a delightful space for comfortable dining. This level also houses a cozy fireplace providing an ideal setting for entertaining friends and family. Descend to the lower level, where you'll discover a versatile bonus room that can be customized to suit your needs. This level also has a laundry closet space and the owner's suite that gives an oasis feel with a nice-sized room with bathroom that leads to your walk-in oversized closet. A private backyard that invites you to unwind and host memorable gatherings. The abundance of natural light throughout the home creates a warm and welcoming ambiance, making each room feel inviting and comfortable. Conveniently located with direct access to Interstate 75 this home offers a haven of comfort. Don't miss the opportunity to make this well-maintained split-level residence your new home, where function meets style in a perfect blend. Schedule a tour TODAY!
